Default to a **mobile-first** layout using existing tokens/themes. Keep SSR/SSG boundaries intact and avoid new deps.

- Reuse `design-tokens.css`, `themes/*`, `globals.css`.
- Do not access `window` in server components.
- Prefer fluid sizing (`clamp`, `%`, `auto`) over fixed px.
- Respect dark mode classes/variables.

## Grid visibility & section-grid rule

**Make desktop grids appear only from `md` up**. Do not force grid on mobile:

```css
/* sections.css */
.section-grid {
  /* mobile: no display so it can be hidden or stack */
  gap: var(--grid-gap-lg, var(--spacing-7));
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .section-grid { display: grid; }
}

/* column helpers remain responsive */
.section-grid-2 { @apply grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2; }
.section-grid-3 { @apply grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3; }
.section-grid-4 { @apply grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4; }
````

